I feel like that right now. I just finished watching Saishuuheiki Kanojo and now im 2 secs from crying (that's a big thing mind you im a guy).<br>
I once saw a Danielle Steel drama and I thought THAT was depressing, but its nothing compared to this. The story and the chars just sucks you right in and leave you horribly broken and depressed afterwards, so I ask any of you:<br>
Have you ever seen something in an anime that compares to what I just described? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=mofo09@polykarbonbbs>mofo09</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://supafly.250free.com/dong-risingkick.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(12/6/03 2:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2628.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://supafly.250free.com/dong-risingkick.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_cry.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: The saddest thing you've ever seen...</span><hr size=1> well in ruroni kenshin ova it was pretty sad when ruroni killed that dude that was gonna get married and how he was thinking in his head that he didnt wanna die and stuff was pretty sad, but then ruroni cut him open!! which was kick ass!!<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=gaarasunakage>Gaara Sunakage</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.geocities.com/gaara_sunakage/Orochimaru.txt" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(12/6/03 3:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2628.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://godkodiak.homestead.com/files/Gaara1.jpg height=79 width=130></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span cla